Class DefaultTimeWindow

java.lang.Object
  vista.time.DefaultTimeWindow
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, TimeWindow
public class DefaultTimeWindow
extends java.lang.Object
implements TimeWindow, java.io.Serializable

Defines a range of time. This is used to specify the range for which the data may be retrieved.
